<th style="background:#b08261; color:#fee8ab; text-align:center; font-size:larger;">
<div style="text-align:center;position:relative;white-space:nowrap;">Sarmatians
<div class="noprint plainlinksneverexpand navbar" style="background:none; padding:0; font-weight:normal;; font-size:xx-small; position:absolute; right:0; top:0; margin:0 5px;"><a href="/wiki/Template:Scythians" title="Template:Scythians"><span title="View this template" style="">v</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="/w/index.php?title=Template_talk:Scythians&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Template talk:Scythians (page does not exist)"><span title="Discussion about this template" style="">d</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Scythians&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Scythians&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow"><span title="Edit this template" style=";">e</span></a></div>
